column23: ""subDepartments"".""deletedAt"" AS ""subDepartments.deletedAt"" FROM ""Department""  ""Department"" INNER JOIN ""Department""  ""subDepartments"" ON ""Department"".""id"" = ""subDepartments"".""parentId"" AND (""subDepartments"".""deletedAt"" IS NULL) WHERE (""Department"".""deletedAt"" IS NULL)"
